{
  "stem": "9168.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Goering's trial had ended in-- on August 31st, 1946.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Goering had committed suicide in October--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "October 10 or 16?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My golly--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was October 16th. 10 of the major Nazi defendants had been sentenced to death by hanging, including Martin Bormann in absentia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on October 16th-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] October 16th, four hours before Goering was to be hanged, he swallowed a cyanide capsule, which was a terrible shock to everyone in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gary, I am-- you know, thinking, I hope I'm getting my figures right here about the major Nazi leaders who were sentenced to death by hanging.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the trials.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- and I'm thinking now that it was 12 sentenced to death by hanging, and 10 were hanged.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I actually must have started working on the trials, I would say, within three or four days of the time I arrived.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Nazi Doctors' Trial actually started on October 25, 1946.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I arrived in Nuremberg on November 6.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I do not remember whether the actual opening statements had started.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The indictments had been filed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All of the pleas had been taken, I believe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I just do not remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I know I was right in with the other reporters, and I was happy to be on the Doctors' Trial while other reporters in that office-- and we had about 24 to 26-- were assigned to other trials.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The whole environment [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] seemed to be filled with some kind of horror.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the courtroom at the Palace of Justice had been bombed, and there was extensive damage, I understood.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
